'''Longnose''' and [[Scarcheek]] were the nicknames given by [[Jaina Solo Fel|Jaina Solo]] to the two hit-[[Squib/Legends|Squibs]] who tried to kill her on [[Tenupe]]. He revealed that [[Emala]], [[Sligh]], and [[Grees]] were the heads of the family and his great-great-great grandparents. When Jaina told the [[Mollom]] to let them go, they took it literally and flung the two hit-Squibs onto the [[Chiss/Legends|Chiss]]' island with their trebuchets.

